c: 47
v: 12
t: "'in allah yudkhil aladhin amanuu biallah warasulih waeamiluu alsaalihat janaat tajri min taht ashjarha al'anhar takrimatan lhm, wamathal aladhin kafaruu fi aklhm wtmtehm baldnya, kamathal al'aneam min albhaym alty la hmm laha 'illa fi alaetlaf dun ghyrh, wnar jahanam maskan lahum wmawa"